hints.content:
Draw $50$ circles, with $5$ to each row.

[[☃ image 1]]

options.alt: Fifty circles arranged in rows of 5 circles each. Circles in the first top row are labeled 1 through 5, circles in the next row are labeled 6 through 10, circles in the next row are labeled 11 through 15, circles in the next row are labeled 16 through 20, circles in the next row are labeled 21 through 25, circles in the next row are labeled 26 through 30, circles in the next row are labeled 31 through 35, circles in the next row are labeled 36 through 40, circles in the next row are labeled 41 through 45, and circles in the last bottom row are labeled 46 through 50. !
